txt.en: A drake-matron resides within the western valley of Ram Dúath. The pass will not be safe until she is slain.

A drake-matron has made her lair in the valley north of Nan Amlug. Even here, you feel her wrath bent upon any who dare set foot in her domain.\n\nYou should defeat the matron who has filled the valley with her brood.

The drake-matron resides within the western pass of Ram Dúath, north-east of Esteldín.\n\nYou should slay the drake-matron of the Ram Dúath. As long as she lives, she will only spawn more worms to cover the land in filth.
You have defeated the drake-matron in the valley of worms, and the northern canyons of Ram Dúath are safer for it.
